{"tid":860652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［東大嶼填海］ 1,700公頃住100萬人 人口密度高過油尖旺 全港第二 19:天方夜譚","createTime":"2018-10-13T13:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T10:30:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0f80a3412d9767a9fddcb3fdeb24ec23c113f2f7","tid":860652,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"1700公頃=17平方公里<br />\n1,000,000人 / 17 = <strong>58,824</strong>/平方公里<br />\n根據政府2017年數字，僅低過觀塘59k人少少<br />\n高過油尖旺48k一大截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/213151_d10f8d653e466d7f66e88bcf96b82d45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F213151_d10f8d653e466d7f66e88bcf96b82d45.png&h=ddb88e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/D5320189B2017AN17B.xls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statistics.gov.hk%2Fpub%2FD5320189B2017AN17B.xls&d=nFMIurY5aehS8viB9UIe%2FDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e45c3221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.statistics.gov.hk/pub/D5320189B2017AN17B.xls</a><br />\n<br />\n100萬人=3個油尖旺<br />\n人工島既交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【陶傑開talk】既有大灣區為何造人工島 林鄭擺明話大灣區冇吸引力｜壹週刊<br />\n<br />\n這個施政報告的重頭戲就是，特區政府聲稱最少沒有五千億都找不到數。<span style=\"color: red;\">這個東大嶼山填海大計安置100-170萬人口，是頗天方夜譚。如果是這樣，像整個旺角的大小，全球密度最高的一度二十多萬人口。填出來的地方如有一百萬人口，即是五個旺角的大小，會需要有很多基建和屏風樓。所以如果把數字吹噓得太大會令人質疑。</span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭對於填海工程表現失手，忘記同時與大灣區有密切的邏輯關係，無形中承認大灣區的吸引力很不濟，是基本邏輯問題。現在公佈填海，是在大灣區大計之內，先告訴我們香港人將來會成為大灣區人，一批批可以北上遷移上大灣區。既然有這個大計，就沒有填海的必要，因為既然香港腹地是珠海、中山及整個大灣區的話，還需要在港取地嗎？<br />\n<br />\n所以我一直以為，既然有大灣區，香港會吸納的大灣區，就不用再填海取地。如香港特區政府宣傳大灣區很美好，有充足的生活設施，一日來回。<br />\n<br />\n香港的土地問題隨著大灣區計劃的開展，一勞永逸，其實已解決問題，這才是最大的矛盾。所以在十年前、二十年前提出，都還好，現在已建成。現在才提出，便與大灣區撞正，及每天一百五十個的新移民配額，從沒提起。將這五千億花在這裡，我認為沒太大意義。<br />\n<br />\n【陶傑開talk】明日大嶼計劃明日好「大鑊」 陶傑：政府慣性超支埋單過萬億<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2A6cnUz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2A6cnUz&d=nFMIurY5aehS8viB9UIe%2FDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ffbd59cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2A6cnUz</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181013/630440?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181013%2F630440%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=nFMIurY5aehS8viB9UIe%2FDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bec496d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181013%2F630440%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e096f86f\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181013/630440?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"d389a4e4ed7eade150078e1448746e6caf679782","tid":860652,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"都好過住劏房"},{"pid":"c6beb1772bbe043eb9360376c53e6db3bbeafcbd","tid":860652,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d389a4e4ed7eade150078e1448746e6caf679782","tid":860652,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"都好過住劏房"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:38:19.000Z","msg":"係根本唔可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ea1d8803b10c5e6c021e9ced7e22d009dda819","tid":860652,"uid":13503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"成個計劃同高鐵一樣都係政治工程，目的並非解決香港民生問題而係解決大陸產能過剩問題"},{"pid":"49e27dc9d48b80e501619a3e83eb6c23df2dbb13","tid":860652,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3fdfc38f3351149f2c55cde3fbf61e77a919a3","tid":860652,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"鳩吹都唔比？"},{"pid":"544b7317cfc01c56bfd77bece7478194e9415bdf","tid":860652,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c3fdfc38f3351149f2c55cde3fbf61e77a919a3","tid":860652,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"鳩吹都唔比？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"政府施政報告比鳩吹? 鳩吹治港?"},{"pid":"57742a1238794e67ccb6b7e5a6a2636061375271","tid":860652,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"544b7317cfc01c56bfd77bece7478194e9415bdf","tid":860652,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c3fdfc38f3351149f2c55cde3fbf61e77a919a3","tid":860652,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"鳩吹都唔比？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"政府施政報告比鳩吹? 鳩吹治港?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"第一日識呢個政府？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}